  - Printable PDF export (with page previews and metadata).
  - Asset bundle (flashcards/answer keys) as a ZIP or multi-format bundle.
- Both exports include a secure, expiring download link. The user can copy or click to download.
- The user can save/export metadata to a study folder or share links with guardians/teachers if allowed.

4) Asset Bundle Preview & Management
- On page_p009, the user can preview flashcards and answer keys in a printable view, toggle options, and re-run a bundle generation if needed.
